<br>
Do not stress.  Those whom <!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b>  have already posted an application</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> are still currently in the que, and we are processing and discussing your possible inclusion to the LCG.<br>
<br>
Over the next couple of days, the remaining threads on the LCG boards regarding application will be moving to this forum, both past and present.  We will update as to the status of each applicant as the process progresses.<br>
<br>
<br>
Thank you,<br>
<br>
on behalf of the LCG Council,<br>
<br>
